item.title: Blow it up kart game
item.description: Heroes of the game Blow up this kart - wonderful robots living in a magical land, organized a racing tournament and invite you to take part in it. Choose one of the characters and hurry to the starting grid of an exciting competition. In each of the races you need not only to overtake your rivals, but also to complete a certain task. Don’t forget to collect bonus badges on the track, which will help to delay your competitors for a while.
